{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Birkeanu, I'd say, a few months, five months or maybe four months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- Buna, I think we were transported in trucks, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was quite a few hundred that went there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was like in the movies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- I-- I was [? shocked ?] and then we saw again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I started to see him, we grabbed at each other and we crying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't separate [? his side. ?] It was a [INAUDIBLE] moment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a moment to never forget it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was in Buna already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were already assigned to a barrack already in Buna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he came-- he heard that people came in from Auschwitz, so he wanted to see and we met again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he-- he-- he was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what happened in the-- there was a lot of-- in-- in-- in Buna-- kapos that were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They German's murderers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Murdered-- they were Gentiles, but they murdered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Instead of sending them to jail, they sent them to take care of us and being a kapo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other ones-- there were other ones with red-- red markings, just like Commie or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But those murderers were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were hitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, you know, one kapo came out one time, and the commander was assigned was commander number was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means two.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number two is in German [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I worked outside, very hard work, and then he-- he asked if somebody can take care of socks, knit socks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had-- [LAUGHS] I knew something about it in school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
